@node intro "Introduction"
     

     This is a Lunar Landing clone game. Your mission is the successfull
     landing on the right place .(see @{" Usage " link use} )
       The program is (fully) OS-friendly .(Multitask)
     You can develop ! (see @{ " Developers " link dev})


@endnode

@node install "Installation"


                           Manual installation :-)
                           ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   
   This program requires 1Mb free space on your HD .

   If there is no @{b}iff.library@{ub} in your LIBS: copy from archive .
  
   If the speech mode is active :(see  @{" Configuration " link config} )
      If there is no @{b}narrator.device@{ub} in your DEVS: copy from your 
     Workbench (WB1.3/WB2.0)
      If there is no @{b}translator.library@{ub} in your LIBS: copy from your
     Workbench. 

  
@endnode
