@node use "Usage"

  Mission:
  ~~~~~~~~

      Your mission is to fly the ship and land succesfully.

      The following things can prevent you from succeding the mission :
      - Obstacles ( If you bump against them -> No Landing Here !)
      - Screen borders ( If you bump against them -> Out Of Space !)
      - Gravity (Newton rulez !)
      - Friction ( There is no ;-)
      - Countdown ( You have limited time -> Out Of Time !)
      - Landing speed (High speed -> Kamikazee Speed !)
      - LIVES ( Game Over )

      @{b}If landing speed < 5 : Bonus Life @{ub}

   Control:
   ~~~~~~~~
    Keyboard mode : (see @{" Configuration " link config} )
        (Cursor keys)
        Up arrow    = force up
        Left arrow  = force right  :-)
        Right arrow = force left   :-)
        Space       = start game, next level
        Esc         = exit (You can only quit on the first screen !)

    Joystick mode : (see @{" Configuration " link config} )
        Down         = force up
        Left         = force right  :-)
        Right        = force left   :-)
        Fire         = start game, next level
        Esc (key)    = exit (You can only quit on the first screen !)


   
    
@endnode

@node config "Configuration"


     This game can be configured by Tooltypes .

     These are the followings :
 
     @{b}Control@{ub}=Keyboard/Joystick
         Control mode .
     @{b}Hardness@{ub}=Easy/Medium/Hard .
         The acceptable landing speed can be set :
         Easy   -> 30
         Medium -> 20
         Hard   -> 10
     @{b}TaskPri@{ub}=-128-127
         Set the task priority of game. Default is 127.
         (When the ship flyes, otherwise 0) 
     @{b}Say@{ub}=On/Off
         Turn On/Off the speech mode.
     @{b}MaxLevel@{ub}=1-x
         Set the number of levels.(Only registered version!)
                     (  see @{ " Registration " link regis})

     If you don`t start from workbench, the game runs with defaults:

          Control=Keyboard
          Hardness=Easy
          TaskPri=127
          Say=Off
          MaxLevel=10 (Unregistered version -> MaxLevel=3 !)     
                       (see @{ " Registration " link regis})
    
@endnode

